A curious rhinoceros made of glowing amber circuitry and metallic chrome plates, standing in a neon-lit digital landscape, examining floating translucent data cubes that orbit around its horn. The rhino's body transitions from organic skin on one side to exposed mechanical components and fiber optic cables on the other. Electric blue and hot pink light streams pulse through the environment, reflecting off wet pavement below. In the background, towering server stacks form a cyberpunk cityscape with holographic Japanese characters floating between them. The rhino's eyes glow with intelligent green light as streams of code-like particles flow from its nostrils. Moody atmosphere with fog and volumetric lighting.
